---
import '../../styles/global.css';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html class="scroll-smooth" lang="en"><head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Cloud Architect &amp; DevOps Lead | Sky Editorial</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

<style>
        .material-symbols-outlined {
            font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 0, 'wght' 400, 'GRAD' 0, 'opsz' 24;
        }
        .upward-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to top, #ffffff, #d3e2ed);
        }
        .soft-elevation {
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -5px rgba(15, 29, 37, 0.04);
        }
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(186, 201, 211, 0.2);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-background text-on-background font-body-md selection:bg-primary-fixed selection:text-on-primary-fixed">
<!-- TopAppBar -->
<Header />
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden upward-gradient pt-24 pb-section-gap">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16 relative z-10">
<div class="flex-1 space-y-8">
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container font-label-sm text-label-sm">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="verified">verified</span>
                    ADVANCED CLOUD TRACK
                </div>
<h1 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-on-surface leading-tight">
                    Cloud Infrastructure <span class="text-primary">Master</span>
</h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl">
                    Transcend traditional DevOps. Build resilient, hyper-scaled architectural legacies with the global standard in cloud orchestration and engineering excellence.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
<button class="px-10 py-4 bg-primary text-white rounded-xl font-label-md text-label-md shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:translate-y-[-2px] transition-all flex items-center gap-2">
                        Enroll Now <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
<button class="px-10 py-4 bg-secondary-container text-primary rounded-xl font-label-md text-label-md hover:bg-secondary-fixed-dim transition-all">
                        Download Syllabus
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-2xl">
<div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
<video autoplay loop muted playsinline class="w-full aspect-video object-cover">
<source src="/admin/devops%20hero%20section.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/40 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Abstract Background Detail -->
<div class="absolute -bottom-48 -left-48 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-fixed-dim/30 rounded-full blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>
</section>
<!-- Trusted By -->
<section class="bg-white py-12 border-y border-outline-variant">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<p class="text-center font-label-sm text-label-sm text-on-surface-variant mb-8 tracking-widest uppercase">Trusted by Global Infrastructure Leaders</p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-12 md:gap-24 opacity-50 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-500">
<div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-on-surface-variant">TechCorp</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-on-surface-variant italic">Globo</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-on-surface-variant tracking-tighter">NEXUS</div>
<div class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-on-surface-variant">CloudFlow</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Microsoft Certification Prep -->
<section class="py-section-gap bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12 bg-white rounded-[32px] p-8 md:p-16 soft-elevation">
<div class="flex-1 space-y-6">
<div class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md">OFFICIAL PARTNER CURRICULUM</div>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface">Microsoft AZ-900 &amp; DP-900 Certification Track</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                        Our program integrates the full Microsoft Azure Fundamentals and Data Fundamentals curriculum. Graduate with not only the Sky States diploma but also industry-recognized credentials from Microsoft at no extra cost.
                    </p>
<ul class="space-y-3">
<li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-on-surface font-label-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span>
                            Complimentary Exam Vouchers
                        </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-on-surface font-label-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span>
                            24/7 Sandbox Labs for Azure
                        </li>
<li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-on-surface font-label-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span>
                            Certified Microsoft Instructor Support
                        </li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="bg-primary/5 rounded-3xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center border border-primary/10 w-full md:w-1/3">
<img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="640" height="453" alt="Microsoft DevOps Certification" class="w-full ambient-shadow rounded-2xl" src="https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops.png" srcset="https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops-1024x724.png 1024w, https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops-300x212.png 300w, https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops-768x543.png 768w, https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops-1536x1086.png 1536w, https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops-600x424.png 600w, https://skystates.us/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/devops.png 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" />
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Why Choose Sky States -->
<section class="py-section-gap">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-4">The Pillars of Program Excellence</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto">Founded on the principle of institutional authority, our pillars ensure your career transition is seamless and superior.</p>
</div>
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter">
<div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation flex flex-col gap-4 border-t-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" data-icon="groups">groups</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Industry-First Mentorship</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Direct access to Lead Architects from Fortune 100 technology firms.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation flex flex-col gap-4 border-t-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" data-icon="terminal">terminal</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Project-Based Learning</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Build enterprise-grade infrastructure, not just theoretical models.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation flex flex-col gap-4 border-t-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" data-icon="podcasts">podcasts</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Live Instruction</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Real-time engagement with instructors for dynamic problem solving.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation flex flex-col gap-4 border-t-4 border-primary">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" data-icon="person_pin">person_pin</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">One-on-One Support</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Tailored guidance to overcome your specific learning bottlenecks.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Is This Right For You? -->
<section class="py-section-gap bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-center mb-16 text-on-surface">Is This Program Right For You?</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
<!-- Who This Program Is For -->
<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border-t-8 border-primary shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-6">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" data-icon="check_circle">check_circle</span>
Who This Program Is For
</h3>
<ul class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
• Professionals aiming for senior leadership roles in cloud infrastructure.
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
• Software Engineers looking to pivot from code to massive-scale cloud infrastructure.
</li>
</ul>
</div>

<!-- Who This Is NOT For -->
<div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl border-t-8 border-outline shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-6">
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-on-surface mb-2 flex items-center gap-3">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-error" data-icon="cancel">cancel</span>
Who This Is NOT For
</h3>
<ul class="space-y-4 text-on-surface-variant font-body-md">
<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
• Those looking for 2-week quick fixes; this is a rigorous, senior-level program.
</li>
<li class="flex items-start gap-2">
• Those looking for theoretical-only academies; we prioritize hands-on engineering.
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- ROI of Excellence -->
<section class="py-section-gap">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop text-center">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-16">The Quantifiable Advantage</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter">
<div class="p-12 glass-card rounded-3xl text-center space-y-4">
<div class="text-primary font-headline-xl text-headline-xl font-extrabold">94%</div>
<p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Placement Rate</p>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Our graduates find placement within 6 months of program completion at top global firms.</p>
</div>
<div class="p-12 glass-card rounded-3xl text-center space-y-4">
<div class="text-primary font-headline-xl text-headline-xl font-extrabold">140%</div>
<p class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-on-surface">Avg Salary Hike</p>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">The average salary increase reported by alumni transitioning from Junior to Lead roles.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Program Curriculum -->
<section class="py-section-gap max-w-4xl mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-gutter" id="curriculum">
<div class="text-center mb-12">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface mb-4">Program Curriculum</h2>
<div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
</div>
<div class="space-y-4">
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all" open="">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">01</span> Module 1: Introduction to DevOps
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Understand the principles and benefits of DevOps, including collaboration between development and operations teams. Learn about the DevOps lifecycle and key tools to enhance software delivery.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">02</span> Module 2: Cloud Computing Fundamentals
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Explore the core concepts of cloud computing, such as virtualization, scalability, and elasticity. Learn about cloud service models (IaaS, PaaS, SaaS) and deployment models (public, private, hybrid).</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">03</span> Module 3: Version Control Systems
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Master Git and other version control systems to track changes in source code. Learn branching, merging, and collaboration techniques to streamline team workflows.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">04</span> Module 4: Continuous Integration and Delivery
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Dive into CI/CD pipelines to automate code integration, testing, and deployment. Learn tools like Jenkins, GitHub Actions, and Azure DevOps to build robust CI/CD workflows.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">05</span> Module 5: Containerization with Docker
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Learn to create, deploy, and manage containers using Docker. Understand containerization concepts, including images, containers, volumes, and networking.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">06</span> Module 6: Orchestration with Kubernetes
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Explore Kubernetes for automating deployment, scaling, and managing containerized applications. Learn about pods, services, deployments, and monitoring clusters.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">07</span> Module 7: Infrastructure as Code (IaC)
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Discover tools like Terraform and CloudFormation to define and provision infrastructure programmatically. Learn best practices for managing infrastructure in a cloud environment.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">08</span> Module 8: Cloud Platforms Overview
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Gain hands-on experience with leading cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, and Google Cloud. Learn core services such as compute, storage, and networking.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">09</span> Module 9: Monitoring and Logging
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Understand the importance of monitoring and logging in maintaining system health. Explore tools like Prometheus, Grafana, and ELK Stack to analyze system performance.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">10</span> Module 10: Security in DevOps
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Integrate security into the DevOps process with DevSecOps practices. Learn about securing CI/CD pipelines, monitoring vulnerabilities, and implementing access controls.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">11</span> Module 11: Hybrid and Multi-Cloud Environments
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Learn strategies for managing applications across hybrid and multi-cloud setups. Explore tools and frameworks for seamless integration between cloud providers.</p>
</div>
</details>
<details class="group bg-white rounded-2xl soft-elevation p-6 cursor-pointer border-l-4 border-transparent open:border-primary transition-all">
<summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface list-none">
<span class="font-headline-md text-headline-md flex items-center gap-4">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">12</span> Module 12: Domain Wise Capstone Project
</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" data-icon="expand_more">expand_more</span>
</summary>
<div class="mt-4 font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed border-t border-outline-variant/30 pt-4">
<p>Apply the knowledge gained throughout the course to complete a real-world project. Design and implement a CI/CD pipeline, containerized application, and monitoring solution in a cloud environment.</p>
</div>
</details>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Innovation Lab -->
<section class="py-section-gap bg-surface-container">
<div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-12">
<div>
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-on-surface">Innovation Lab</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Core projects you will engineer during the program.</p>
</div>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-1 hover:underline">View Portfolio Hub <span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="open_in_new">open_in_new</span></button>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter">
<div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl aspect-[16/10] bg-on-surface">
