<div class="absolute bottom-8 left-8 right-8 z-20 space-y-2">
<h4 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white">Predictive Infrastructure Engine</h4>
<p class="text-white/70 font-body-md text-body-md">Machine learning models that auto-scale resources based on traffic forecasting.</p>
